high_descs: Walk straight towards the curtain and turn to the drawer on your left.
Pick up the pencil on the drawer.
Move towards the plate on the drawer.
Put the pencil in the plate on the drawer.
Pick up the plate with the pencil on the drawer.
Turn around and turn around again and go to the shelf on your left.
Put the plate with the pencil on the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a pencil on a shelf.

high_descs: Head to the dresser on the left.
Pick up the pencil from the dresser.
Turn to face the plate on the dresser.
Put the pencil on the plate on the dresser.
Pick up the plate with the pencil from the dresser.
Head to the shelf on the left.
Put the plate on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with the pencil on the shelf.

high_descs: turn around and walk over to the dresser.
pick up the pencil from the dresser.
turn around and look at the dresser.
put the pencil in the plate in the dresser.
pick up the plate from the dresser.
walk over to the shelf.
put the plate on the shelf.
